{"tid":2444742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府拒發指引 許樹昌：世衞也無準則","createTime":"2021-03-13T05:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T06:39:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"19b1e32ea788850750cbb18bbcc224ac5777287c","tid":2444742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210313/ZFSLSO56Z5AEHGHYLBGLTEQY3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210313%2FZFSLSO56Z5AEHGHYLBGLTEQY3Y%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=916712a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210313%2FZFSLSO56Z5AEHGHYLBGLTEQY3Y%2F&h=6547d6b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210313/ZFSLSO56Z5AEHGHYLBGLTEQY3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府拒發指引 許樹昌：世衞也無準則<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y06NBtfooM112Tl29Fnf6ErIEn8=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VVCYEILPBZGE5OLUZIW7CDLO6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy06NBtfooM112Tl29Fnf6ErIEn8%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVVCYEILPBZGE5OLUZIW7CDLO6I.jpg&h=d5ef42a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多名市民接種疫苗後感不適；圖為本月8日一名婦人注射科興疫苗後心悸送院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】外界批評政府接種疫苗指引不清晰，一度有消息指，衞生署昨日會發出具體接種疫苗指引，但最終未見指引出爐，取而代之是香港內科醫學院發表的聲明，內容極簡單，僅指若慢性病患者感到不適，或其醫療狀況未受控，便應押後接種。學院委員解釋，現無科學證據證明血壓或血糖指數超過某指數，便不宜接種疫苗，若以劃一數字作界線「會累咗好多人冇得打」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：議員轟賠償標準含糊 龍門任搬<br />\n<br />\n疫苗顧問專家委員會成員孔繁毅日前接受D100網台訪問時透露，衞生署將發出指引表列不適合接種武肺疫苗的情況，供私家醫生及市民參考；例如列明血壓長期達160/100以上，血糖HbA1C數值長期達10以上等，均不適合或須延遲接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劃一「累好多人冇得打」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，衞生署早前諮詢內科醫學院制訂指引的意見，但學院前日開會，有共識認為難以單一數字決定是否適合接種疫苗，故最終衞生署沒有發出相關指引，取而代之由內科醫學院作出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：衞署報告：47人入院全接種國產針  首宗打科興面癱 瞞足一周<br />\n<br />\n有關聲明指出三點，包括學院鼓勵公眾接種疫苗；慢性病患者接種疫苗帶來的好處，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內科醫學院委員許樹昌表示，世衞、美國疾控中心及新加坡等海外內科機構。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌續稱，無科學數據證明血壓或血糖超過某個指數，便不宜接種或接種不安全，很多長者因血管硬化，上壓會超過150或160。。。。。"},{"pid":"412e0ad1bca83289c412bd4797a05bab510bf06a","tid":2444742,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"因支衞同港共一鳩樣"},{"pid":"9b92aa9687a7f435cc28662f127946ff9358bd35","tid":2444742,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"錯的是世界"},{"pid":"1ba26bb65936d0d346f7828e376cd12cc658419a","tid":2444742,"uid":156913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"人地食屎又唔見你食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bad301d49058e307e626d22bde1fddeecdf823","tid":2444742,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"世衞都冇批科興<br />\n點會有準則"},{"pid":"1bbbbf18eb32f640e69211c282aeb5fc567abc81","tid":2444742,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"科興生物在1999年創立，公司股權轉換巳數唔哂咁多次，睇到頭都暈，又豬流感，雞瘟，黑死病(疫苗)&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />轉呀轉，一定係好嘢"},{"pid":"d0f50d2725d1c3b460854b4c6f2e5de16d4b66f7","tid":2444742,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"許樹娼呢隻奶共賤畜真係不得好死<br />\n支那60歲唔打得科興咪又係劃一<br />\n用血壓血糖做標準反而仲科學"},{"pid":"b17b9e409ce1457ce5055a67650e2f0ccecb3dd6","tid":2444742,"uid":26611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"究竟 比下限依個風氣係幾時開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bff9aee84c8a7bee5cbf6d3c6c8a957d05c09a4","tid